{"tid":2510583,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"個股跟蹤：Teladoc 2021Q1業績","createTime":"2021-04-30T09:08:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T09:12:22.000Z","uid":359715,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5b4a9c2f2ece5b67ed5cdfd97b2fa9faba4ab075","tid":2510583,"uid":359715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:08:23.000Z","msg":"Teladoc公佈第一季度業績<br />\n- 營收4.53億美元，同比增長151%（勝預期4.51億美元）<br />\n- 每股淨虧損（1.31美元）遜於預期的（0.62美元）<br />\n- EBITDA由去年Q1 1070萬美元大幅增加至5660萬美元<br />\n- 問診次數按季提昇8%至320萬次<br />\n- 使用率由上季17.7%增加至19.6%<br />\n管理層預計全年營收可達19.7億至20.2億美元，與之前預計的情況相若。業績反映公司仍然on the right track，Teladoc仍在高速增長的軌道上，期望收購Livongo之後的協同效應進一步突顯，在疫情後繼續保持增長及競爭優勢：<a href=\"https://luk-mall-invest.blogspot.com/2021/04/teladoc.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fluk-mall-invest.blogspot.com%2F2021%2F04%2Fteladoc.html&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT8bSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=0dcabcc5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://luk-mall-invest.blogspot.com/2021/04/teladoc.html</a>"},{"pid":"32ede66a0a2c1f7333a3554a492022b83870c16c","tid":2510583,"uid":357651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:12:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}